snippet.title: A Creative Bible Journaling Study of GENESIS 21:8-21 with Amber Bolton of the Inspire Bible TOUR
snippet.description:
Feeling "Inspired?" Visit: http://bit.ly/2CkrpHv
Like, comment, and subscribe for more inspiring videos!
Join Amber Bolton of the Inspire Bible TOUR as she helps you be creative and connected with God’s Word. Grab your Bible and favorite Bible journaling supplies and follow along with Amber as she guides you through her 4-step Bible study process. She will also share tips, techniques, and favorite Bible journaling supplies to equip and encourage you to respond creatively in the margins of your Bible. This video is sponsored by Tyndale House Publishers and features the Inspire Bible for Girls softcover edition, ISBN 978-1-4964-2661-1. Enjoy your time in God’s Word!
